<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="hit-on-upon">hit on / upon</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-come-up-with">1.<strong>突然想到 (come up with)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>hit on / upon an idea 
想出一个主意</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>At last we hit on a way out of this difficulty.
我们终于想出了一个解决这个困难的办法。</p></div></div>